\id 2TI - Sembeleke Samberigi PNG 2Timothy 01 13/2/91 Macnaughtan 
\h 2 TIMODI 
\toc1 Polomaęž‰ Timodi paęž‰taęž‰ yaapo peao wape pea tapaeyekeeki 
\toc2 2 Timodi 
\toc3 2 Timodi 
\mt1 Polomaęž‰ Timodi paęž‰taęž‰ yaapo peao wape pea tapaeyekeeki  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Polo IĚ±taęž‰ mo Ketiso Yesunaęž‰ aposolo hali halome. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ laęž‰ wieke deto halaęž‰eki Ketiso Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ molomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ pi walono yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± maĚ±leke lia tapaalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 2 Do wapetaęž‰ ya pukipiki weki Timodi neke paęž‰taęž‰ wape pitolome. Mo Apaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ pitaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu nikaęž‰ Tekehali ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make puki lopaasaęž‰eki make neke paęž‰taęž‰ kinaęž‰e.   
\s1 Keiyae pi pitaęž‰ hone u tiaasaęž‰ pi yaapo  
\p
\v 3 Ya apaęž‰naęž‰ atekenaęž‰ atekemaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao hao haemeke tupaęž‰ IĚ± make ya hone tekemaęž‰ alaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na taĚ±leĚ±naęž‰ leke koto tupaęž‰ kone hone tulao halome. IĚ±maęž‰ timba make natenaęž‰ make neke hone na yonkaęž‰lake Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitolo keiyae pi lo halome.  
\v 4 Mo nakaęž‰ leke paęž‰taęž‰ eĚ± pankeke lopo hayaęž‰eki handoaęž‰eki niminaaso hataęž‰ neke handuluekemaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ paęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu puaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰ tiekemaęž‰ homulueke.  
\v 5 Mo nakaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone tulale ekitaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ niminao halome. Nakaęž‰ aeyaęž‰ Loisi pitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ amaęž‰ Yunisi yaapomaęž‰ make do mandake hone tulaepe ekitaęž‰ ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ make taa ulaęž‰me.  
\v 6 Koto hone uaęž‰eki tekenaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ nakaęž‰ younaęž‰ ya kiki uaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ pa hameke kaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ alupaamaęž‰naęž‰ halimaęž‰ ti honiaamaęž‰naęž‰ po lo halaęž‰ tupaęž‰ kone do hautaęž‰ pa mea tiaaso tiaaso halenaęž‰ hone u tiaasome.  
\v 7 Pa ekipeke. Mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰taęž‰ niki yalaęž‰ yalaęž‰ na peaasaęž‰me. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Sipitidimaęž‰ mo wele pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make hone lu tumbaasaęž‰eki make niki anaęž‰naęž‰ ku halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 8 Mo nikaęž‰ Tekehalinaęž‰ pi walawasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Kutaa make IĚ± mo Ketisonaęž‰ e pokawaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ dipula mea pitaalemeke pilu ekinaęž‰ neke yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homaęž‰peke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ wele tapu hataęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo walaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± yaapo mandake mea tia hapanaęž‰e.  
\v 9 Nikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hamono yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ mea wi laęž‰laęž‰me. Koto hau pieke ekinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ nikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke hau pumaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ diaęž‰pate pa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ ipikaęž‰ hone pieke ekimaęž‰ kone niki wi laęž‰laęž‰me. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ do kenke aĚ±iĚ± na wepia winaęž‰ leeke pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ do aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ niki miomono yeke Ketiso Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ winaęž‰ leekeme.  
\v 10 Pate ametaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰ hali Ketiso Yesu ipikaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰eki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ peneme yaalaęž‰me. Mo homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ wele ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ paeyaaso hataęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ Pi Seliapo paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ deto halaęž‰eki peneme yaalaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 11 Koto Pi Seliaponaęž‰ la halaęž‰laęž‰ hali make aposolo hali hataęž‰ mokaęž‰laęž‰ tiaaso hali hano yeke Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± maĚ±leke liaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Kotaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ koto haumanu puaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ame do kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu minolopate pa IĚ±maęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homolome. Pa ekipeke. Mo IĚ±maęž‰ ya hone ti lalo halitaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone ulume. Ya honemaęž‰taęž‰ mo ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± kaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande ipikaęž‰ Nate tieke epenaęž‰yeke anaęž‰naęž‰ handeteke hao hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ pi epeke tupaęž‰ waluekemaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰ pi kone hone wia walaęž‰tiki pu hapeke. Kutu pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ mo Ketiso Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulao pukimaęž‰ homolo hataęž‰ peaęž‰peke.  
\v 14 Mo neke paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ epeke epeke hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ wopu handeteke ke haluekemaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ puki paęž‰taęž‰ pilaęž‰ Holi Sipitidinaęž‰ wele peaasaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ welemaęž‰ wopu handeteke hapeke.   
\p
\v 15 Mo Eisia potopinisi haleme wandaęž‰hali paeyao make mo hande Paidiaęž‰lisi pitaęž‰ Hemodionisi koto hali yaapo tonkaęž‰naęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰lao peleme ekitaęž‰ neke hone wotu witeleme.  
\v 16 Mo hande hali Onesipotasimaęž‰ hoto paeyao IĚ± taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiao hayeke handaa IĚ±maęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wekiwandaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰ honke alome. Pa ekipeke. IĚ± do dipula pilu ekinaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ yaalaęž‰maęž‰ na homeaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kotoeki na piaęž‰pate ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ Lomaęž‰ da opolo aęž‰paataęž‰ koto kone IĚ± weitia pomu haotaęž‰ handaęž‰ wiaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Mo hande Nate tieke opolo epeaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki koto some paęž‰taęž‰ halenaęž‰e. Mo hande Epesese nane haomaęž‰ tomaęž‰naęž‰ Onesipotasimaęž‰ tambaęž‰ mu hataęž‰ piaęž‰ hau paeyaotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ handeleme.   
\c 2  
\s1 Ketiso Yesunaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homa halaęž‰ aęž‰ndeli miniki hali  
\p
\v 1 Ya weki neke paęž‰taęž‰ dupa alome. Mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu ameĚ±leĚ± taęž‰maęž‰ni pitolo hataęž‰ minolomaęž‰me. Koto aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ minele ekinaęž‰taęž‰ honkopu hao hapeke.  
\v 2 IĚ±maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali eleke elekenaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ waloeke opi manaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ kotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ meaataęž‰ mo hone epeke tupaęž‰ u paleke hataęž‰ mandane da wandaęž‰hali anaęž‰naęž‰ walaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mokaęž‰la hale hale peaęž‰peke.   
\p
\v 3 Ketiso Yesunaęž‰ epeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ peaasaęž‰ hali hataęž‰ mo ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ mandaneeki nakanaęž‰maęž‰ meaęž‰peke.  
\v 4 Ami hali homekemaęž‰ ami hali hataęž‰taęž‰ ipikaęž‰ you halinaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ homu haluekemaęž‰ pa mo da wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ pu haleme haumanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ apaęž‰tao na pilieke.  
\v 5 Kutupa make mo telepo tiekemanu lo halaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰ mo teleponaęž‰ pi ulaęž‰ ekimanu na tolu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ tombo watao yenki miaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 6 E handeteke halaęž‰ halimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ e tieke wopu poko halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ mo enaęž‰ ne tanu ekitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰la milieke.  
\v 7 IĚ±maęž‰ alo pitaęž‰ hone wopu wiaęž‰peke. Koto pi hone uelenaęž‰taęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ neke tambaęž‰ milieke.   
\p
\v 8 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo hande homa paa tiaeyeke yeke Deipidinaęž‰ tapake hali Yesu Ketiso hone u hapeke. IĚ±maęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo waloaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ koto pi kone walo halome.  
\v 9 IĚ±maęž‰ do Pi Seliapo walo halo ekinaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tieke mu halome. Kutaa make IĚ±taęž‰ pi yambaęž‰laęž‰laęž‰ hoke hali leke seni pumaęž‰ tonkao uleke halome. IĚ±taęž‰ koto paęž‰leke halopate pa Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pitaęž‰ kutupe seni pumaęž‰ na tonkao ulaęž‰me.  
\v 10 IĚ±maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰maęž‰ maĚ±leke lilaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali tambaęž‰ muluekemaęž‰ do kaęž‰ndaęž‰ paeyaotaęž‰ na kiake mea tu halome. Mo wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ aęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ na paelo paęž‰laęž‰ paĚ±aĚ± tiekemaęž‰ winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ daęž‰taasaęž‰eki minaęž‰yeke IĚ±maęž‰ do kaęž‰ndaęž‰ tu moneao halome.   
\p
\v 11 Dotaęž‰ otaęž‰ pi alo pie.  
\q1 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake aęž‰ndaęž‰ homomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake kone daęž‰taa halumeke.   
\q1
\v 12 Kutupa nikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu epenaęž‰ kone aelaęž‰ bao haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipiki ameĚ±leĚ± mandake piki you wandaęž‰hali kone halumeke.  
\q1 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipiki aęž‰ndaęž‰ kiaomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ niki make kiaalieke.   
\q1
\v 13 Nikanaęž‰maęž‰ nikaęž‰ hone ti lao halumeke laa kone pa hone na ti lao haomaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ kone kotaęž‰ kutu pumonopate pa ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ pulueke laa laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pitaęž‰ otaęž‰ na tunkulieke.  
\q1 Pa ekipeke ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ ipikaęž‰ titinaęž‰ laęž‰ ulaęž‰ pi kialuekemaęž‰ wetepe topo piki pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ lapeke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 14 Do ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hone u tiaaso hataęž‰ la halo hapeke. Kutu pikaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ iki kinki pitolo hataęž‰taęž‰ dupa lapeke. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi teke manunaęž‰ tekenaęž‰taęž‰ pi yokaalu alu pu ape ape na lapaęž‰peke lapeke. Kutu piki haumaęž‰taęž‰ maęž‰ndaęž‰ na tambaęž‰ mulu paęž‰laęž‰pate mo opilimi wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paa hoeyaasaęž‰eki homeke wilieke.   
\s1 Ipikaęž‰ enaęž‰ pi lawaaso haenaęž‰ e pokaęž‰laęž‰ hali  
\p
\v 15 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ otaęž‰ epeke e pokaęž‰laęž‰ hali haluekemaęž‰taęž‰ neke yalaęž‰ peaamaęž‰naęž‰ nakaęž‰ titinaęž‰ honetaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homenaęž‰e hone witolo hataęž‰ e poko hapeke. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pi tikitiki walaęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰taęž‰ koto hau pu hapeke.  
\v 16 Mo wandaęž‰hali Kodaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao papate haenaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰ epe na piki Kodaęž‰ mataake pimanu la kiteme pi manutaęž‰ hoki wala kiao puaęž‰peke.  
\v 17 Koto Kodaęž‰ mataake pi la kitaęž‰laęž‰ pitaęž‰ mo mindiki naęž‰paasaęž‰ bolekemaęž‰ handaęž‰laęž‰me. Kutu piki pitaęž‰ yaapo hali Haimeniasi pitaęž‰ Pailitaęž‰si yaapomaęž‰ walepeme.  
\v 18 Koto hali yaapomaęž‰taęž‰ mo otaęž‰ haumanu minaęž‰paęž‰laepeme. Kutu polo hataęž‰ mo nikaęž‰ homa paa tialo polomaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ ipilikanaęž‰maęž‰ alotaęž‰ Nikitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homa tiao halomaęž‰me alepeme. Koto alepe ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo mandane pi minaęž‰laęž‰ wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ hone tulaaseme ekitaęž‰ hoeyaasepeme.   
\p
\v 19 Kodaęž‰maęž‰ nokopeeke takaęž‰lake pinkitaęž‰ daĚ±oĚ±laęž‰pa paęž‰laęž‰me. Koto pinkinaęž‰ pi yaapo wape pea ulaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ dupa. Tekehalimaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ wandaęž‰halitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ ambaęž‰ hando ulume laa wape pea ulaęž‰me. Kutupa pi maęž‰ndaęž‰ make dupa. Maęž‰ndaęž‰ hali epimaęž‰ IĚ±taęž‰ mo Tekehalinaęž‰eki halome leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ mo hokeeki paeyao otaęž‰ minaęž‰paęž‰lao hoki walaa puaęž‰peke yaęž‰laęž‰me pi yaapo wape paęž‰laęž‰me.   
\p
\v 20 Mo hamoko da tieke paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ paataęž‰ piki make nokaęž‰ wiki kawaso taęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ pikieki wopu ulaęž‰me. Mo kawaso manutaęž‰ silipamaęž‰ make kolomaęž‰ make waęž‰peleme. Kutupa mandane ekitaęž‰ timaęž‰ make kenkemaęž‰ make waęž‰peleme. Do kawaso mandaneeki manutaęž‰ hau tieke pitolo meaęž‰pekeeki winaęž‰ laataęž‰ mandane ekitaęž‰ pa nate paeyao pa mu hapekeeki winaęž‰ laęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 21 Hali maęž‰ndaęž‰ epimaęž‰ mo hoke hau paeyaonaęž‰ haĚ±iĚ± aęž‰ndaęž‰ ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ na taĚ±leĚ±naęž‰ leaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ipikitaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ taęž‰taęž‰ piki hau tieke maęž‰ndaęž‰ peaenaęž‰ mea haenaęž‰ lelieke. Pa ekipeke. Mo somemaęž‰ ipikaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ halaęž‰laęž‰ epeke emanu pokaaluekemaęž‰ tikitiki yao ulaęž‰ ale manumaęž‰ handa halaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 22 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo wekihali hataęž‰ mo wekiwandikimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hoke hone u alualu pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu wendiaęž‰peke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo iki tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ ikaęž‰ yako piki pukimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ Tekehali o laa wi lo haleme wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± hataęž‰ mo tikitiki piki hau make hone tulaasaęž‰eki make pukimaęž‰ homaęž‰laęž‰eki make aęž‰ndaęž‰ peliaasaęž‰eki make muluekemaęž‰ hone ha paleke puaęž‰peke.  
\v 23 Mo teke na wiki o teke na handeke pi yokaalu alu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki manutaęž‰ hoki wala puaęž‰peke. Pa ekipeke. Koto hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ ape ape mea laęž‰tialiekeyeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 24 Mo Tekehalinaęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ ape ape na lelieke. Kotoeki na pikitaęž‰ ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homolo epeke disa hali hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ pu hoeyaaseme haumanu paęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± na homake yu wia hapeke yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 25 Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo pi tunkuleleme wandaęž‰hali tikitiki yaasotaęž‰ kimelemaęž‰ haumaęž‰taęž‰ yopu pu halieke. Koto hau aęž‰ndaęž‰ pu hayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰ waleke wiayaęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ pukimanu topo pea mo otaęž‰ pinaęž‰ hone ti laemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰  
\v 26 kotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemanu paa epeke tupaęž‰ mea lopao wilimikie. Kutu pimikinaęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ Sadaninaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰eki peaenaęž‰ miniki halaęž‰ bisale paęž‰taęž‰ pambelemeeki holaęž‰pa yopua halimikie.   
\c 3  
\s1 Nate paeliaęž‰ tomaęž‰naęž‰ peaęž‰peke yolo paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu  
\p
\v 1 Mo nate paeliaęž‰ tomaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homaasaęž‰ haumanu wopu ipiliekemaęž‰ hone wopu wia hapeke.  
\v 2 Koto paeliaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ do haumanu pu halimikie. Ikitaęž‰ IĚ± IĚ± alo hataęž‰ make pasaęž‰tei hau wopu pitaęž‰laęž‰eki make hakoko liki pimanu lo make handaenaęž‰ honemanu u make yalaęž‰ peaaso hataęž‰ make kikamaęž‰ handeke some alaęž‰ hoke pimanu make lo halimikie. Kutaa make ateke inkikinaęž‰ kakenaęž‰ na homo make keiyae loluekemaęž‰ hone na u make yeni hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu hone na wiki wandaęž‰hali make halimikie.  
\v 3 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ na mu make pa paeyaaluekemaęž‰ hone na u make hoki nane laasaęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hataęž‰ make hone mataęž‰pa pua hataęž‰ wandaęž‰hali hoeyaasaęž‰ hau pu make kika maęž‰naęž‰naęž‰ hau leke pitaęž‰laęž‰ hau make pu halimikie. Mo wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ epeke haumanu honditi pu halimikie.  
\v 4 Kutaa make ikanaęž‰maęž‰ yankeke kone linaęž‰ maęž‰naęž‰ yapaęž‰ mu aęž‰ndaęž‰ lombo make homaęž‰laęž‰ ale teke na hake haumanu pu make ikaęž‰ honemaęž‰ ikitaęž‰ tieke halomaęž‰me hone witolo hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰ pukimaęž‰ na homeketaęž‰ pa ikaęž‰ loke taęž‰naęž‰ peaasaęž‰ alemanu paęž‰taęž‰ pukimaęž‰ homo halememe.  
\v 5 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ yeni pitaęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ pa peaęž‰tiki peaęž‰tiki pu halemepate mo yeninaęž‰ wele pitaęž‰laęž‰ ekitaęž‰ hoki walaa kiaaso halememe. Kutu piki wandaęž‰hali ameĚ±leĚ± apaęž‰tao na hapeke.   
\p
\v 6 Kutu piki mandane haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mandane hone wopu na wiki wandaęž‰weki homu pealuekemaęž‰ ikaęž‰ da paęž‰taęž‰ yopu siki hondaęž‰ pamba pu halememe. Kutu piki wandaęž‰weki ikaęž‰ hoke hau manumaęž‰taęž‰ ikaęž‰ honemanu kaęž‰ndaęž‰ peaotaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lokenaęž‰ hoke hone paęž‰laęž‰eki manumaęž‰ iki yolaęž‰ mea aneya moneya pu halaęž‰me.  
\v 7 Do koto wandaęž‰wekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo pimanu opua hone uluekemaęž‰ taapemekepate pa mo otaęž‰ pinaęž‰ teketaęž‰ miniki hapaęž‰peke na yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 8 Mo hande Diaęž‰nisi pitaęž‰ Diaęž‰mbitisi yaapomaęž‰ Mosesi paęž‰taęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ lipikime. Koto some yaapomaęž‰ pipiki tupaęž‰ kone mo hande haliwekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo hande otaęž‰ pi paęž‰taęž‰ make aęž‰ndaęž‰ lu halememe. Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone tikitiki na yaaso hataęž‰ kone Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaapeke ekinaęž‰taęž‰ iki anaęž‰ na paleke handaataęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ iki kiao halaęž‰me.  
\v 9 Koto haliweki ikaęž‰ hautaęž‰ wopu na daeyalieke. Mo ambaęž‰ haemeke wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo hande Diaęž‰nisi Diaęž‰mbitisi yaaponaęž‰ pambaęž‰ na piki hau pipikieki handolo pimiki tupaęž‰ ame make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ koto haliwekinaęž‰ pambaęž‰ na piki haumanu handilimikie.   
\s1 Paeyaaso manaęž‰ pi  
\p
\v 10 Pate nakanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± yaapo neke mandake pomi pitaęž‰maęž‰taęž‰ mo hande wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ waloaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ ambaęž‰ opua hone wilime. Kutaa ya hau pitaęž‰ ya puaęž‰eki yaapotaęž‰ nakanaęž‰maęž‰ hone wilime. Kutaa IĚ±maęž‰ ya hone tulaaloeki make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ pi minaęž‰ sokaęž‰laęž‰maęž‰ homa na kiake pa handeteke haloeki make ya aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa pukimaęž‰ homoloeki make kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu epenaęž‰ kone IĚ±maęž‰ honkopu hao daĚ±oĚ±la haloeki make nakanaęž‰maęž‰ handeleme.  
\v 11 Mandane haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± lu yombu moneao halemeke make tanda wopunaęž‰ moneao haloeki make handeme. Mo hande Aęž‰ndioko da paęž‰taęž‰ make Aikoniomo da paęž‰taęž‰ make kutaa Lisita da paęž‰taęž‰ make do da tepo haliwekimaęž‰ IĚ± otaęž‰ hoeyaęž‰ hau lu yombu haenaęž‰ kone pa takaęž‰lao haowaęž‰ ekitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone wilime. Kutu pimipate kone mo Tekehalimaęž‰ do koto hau paeyaonaęž‰ tukiki paęž‰taęž‰ kone IĚ± wopu paęž‰taęž‰laęž‰ moneao hayaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Aowe. Koto tupaęž‰ kone mandane wandaęž‰hali epimaęž‰ Ketiso Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ taęž‰maęž‰ni pea hataęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi tolu haemekaęž‰naęž‰taęž‰ kotaęž‰ iki paęž‰taęž‰taęž‰ mandane haliwekimaęž‰ mo hoeyaęž‰ hapu lu yombuaęž‰laęž‰ haumanu pilimikie.  
\v 13 Hoke hau pu halaęž‰ haliweki make yayapiki hau pitaęž‰laęž‰ haliweki make ikaęž‰ ikaęž‰ kone makea alu alu pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ hoke hau manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ mea daeyalimikie.   
\p
\v 14 Kutu pu halimipate neketaęž‰ hande waleeke opi otaęž‰ pimanu wopu miniki hale ekitaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lapeke. Hande neke waleaęž‰ tapaketaęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone wilime.  
\v 15 Kutaa make mo hande Yakopiki Baibolonaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pi manutaęž‰ neke wekisiki hataęž‰ kone kini pea opuaęž‰tiki aęž‰pa ame make paa opuolo haleme. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo Ketiso Yesu paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaaseeki paęž‰taęž‰ yamaęž‰ meaęž‰peke daęž‰taasaęž‰eki muelenaęž‰ u tiaasaęž‰ honetaęž‰ do Baibolonaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pi manumaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 16 Mo Baibolonaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰ pi paeyao wape pinaęž‰taęž‰ haliwekinaęž‰ hone paęž‰taęž‰ Kodaęž‰maęž‰ walaęž‰ tiaaso haenaęž‰ wape pimikime. Koto wape paęž‰laęž‰ pimaęž‰taęž‰ wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu waluekemaęž‰ make hoke hau peaamaęž‰naęž‰ saęž‰saęž‰ puluekemaęž‰ make hoi piki haumanu tondepealuekemaęž‰ make kutupa epeke hapeke ekinaęž‰ manaęž‰manu loluekemaęž‰ wape pea ulaęž‰me.  
\v 17 Kutu peaapeke yaęž‰laęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ somemaęž‰ epeke hau paeyao anaęž‰naęž‰ peaenaęž‰ tikitiki yao haenaęž‰ lelieke.   
\c 4  
\s1 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ otaęž‰ pimanu homeke walo hapeke  
\p
\v 1 Mo pa haleme wandaęž‰hali pitaęž‰ ambaęž‰ homemeke wandaęž‰hali pea telipulu paęž‰laęž‰ Ketiso Yesu pitaęž‰ Kodaęž‰ yaaponaęž‰ leke popelekenaęž‰ telepo pi na alopate Ketisotaęž‰ mo wandaęž‰halinaęž‰ handeteke hao halo paęž‰laęž‰ Kini hali ipiliekeyeke ya pukimaęž‰ kaęž‰ndaęž‰maęž‰ homolo haenaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ neke paęž‰taęž‰ dupaęž‰pekee alome.  
\v 2 Kodaęž‰naęž‰ pi walo hapeke. Kutu polo halenaęž‰ wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ opuluekemaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ na homolo haenaęž‰ make o taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homa opitolo haenaęž‰ make na kiaake pa walolo walolo ombu hapeke. Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ mo puki nalaęž‰ pimaęž‰ make mineke pimaęž‰ make kutupa mo hone u tiaasaęž‰ pimaęž‰ make koto pi manumaęž‰ ikanaęž‰maęž‰ epeke honemanu winaęž‰ loluekemaęž‰ taęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ homaęž‰ tiaaso handeteke hao hapeke.  
\v 3 Wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ mo epeke manaęž‰ pi wopu na opulu paęž‰laęž‰ nate make ipilieke. Kutaa make wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ hone paęž‰laęž‰ ekimanu pitolo hataęž‰ ikaęž‰ opulueke hone peleme pimanu la halaęž‰peke yolo paęž‰laęž‰ haliwekimaęž‰ iki handeteke haenaęž‰ handaęž‰ meaęž‰tiki pilimikie.  
\v 4 Ikanaęž‰maęž‰ pa tindemanu homeke opuluekemaęž‰ mo otaęž‰ pitaęž‰ na opiki hoki walaa kiaalimikie.  
\v 5 Kutu pinaęž‰ kone neke paęž‰taęž‰ ekipiki haumanu epenaęž‰ kone kotaęž‰ koto ekimaęž‰ neke hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰ nakaęž‰ hone lu tombua tombua pitolo hataęž‰ hapeke. Kaęž‰ndaęž‰manu epenaęž‰ kone daĚ±oĚ±la hataęž‰kaęž‰naęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo walaęž‰laęž‰ hali hataęž‰ e poko hapeke. Kutupa neketaęž‰ Kodaęž‰naęž‰ e pokaasaęž‰ hali hataęž‰ nakaęž‰ kaęž‰laęž‰ e poko hapeke.   
\p
\v 6 IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ epolo paęž‰laęž‰ hautaęž‰ dupa. Mo hande hoteke lia halaęž‰laęž‰ tupaęž‰ IĚ± lu peleme natetaęž‰ teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me. IĚ± do kenkenaęž‰ haloeki paeyaalo polo nate teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰laęž‰me.  
\v 7 IĚ±taęž‰ mo hotoneli kitaęž‰laęž‰ ekinaęž‰taęž‰ ya wele paeyaomaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ aĚ±iĚ±ya pua mo tombo epeke tupaęž‰ watao halome. Kutupa make mo ya Kodaęž‰ paęž‰taęž‰ hone tulaalo ekitaęž‰ na minaęž‰paęž‰lalome.  
\v 8 Koto ekinaęž‰ mo tikitiki pea haeme wandaęž‰halimaęž‰ ikaęž‰ lombei pimiki ekinaęž‰ meaęž‰peke yenki tieketaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ putupiliki miono yeke pa ulaęž‰me. Do koto ya lombei polo ekinaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ mo Tekehali nikaęž‰ tikitiki teli peaasaęž‰ halimaęž‰ mo epolo paęž‰laęž‰ nate tiekenaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ kilieke. Koto yenkitaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ homeke na kulu paęž‰laęž‰pate pa mo mandane ipiki peneme yaenaęž‰ yeke pukimaęž‰ homolo handeteke hao haleme wandaęž‰hali paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ halieke.   
\s1 Polonaęž‰ ale manunaęž‰ pimanu  
\p
\v 9 Nakanaęž‰maęž‰ koto kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± ipuluekemaęž‰ taapo hapeke.  
\v 10 Dimasitaęž‰ do kenkenaęž‰ haunaęž‰ hone wopu pieke ekimaęž‰ IĚ± na leeke minaęž‰paęž‰lao mo Desalonaika da nane pua halaęž‰me. Ketesinisitaęž‰ Kaęž‰leisia kenke nane pua halaęž‰me. Taitasitaęž‰ mo Daęž‰lemeisia kenke nane pua halaęž‰me.  
\v 11 Luku homeke homeke IĚ± yaapo halopaęž‰me. Neke ipulu hataęž‰taęž‰ Maka handaęž‰ muaęž‰tiki aęž‰paęž‰peke. Ipikanaęž‰maęž‰ IĚ± tambaęž‰ minaęž‰ yeke loaęž‰me.  
\v 12 Tikikasitaęž‰ Epesese nane tapaowaęž‰me.   
\p
\v 13 Ya kosaęž‰ dautaęž‰ mo Todoaęž‰si da halaęž‰ hali Kapusimaęž‰ wia hawaenaęž‰ epoaęž‰maęž‰ neke ipulu hataęž‰taęž‰ meaęž‰tiki aęž‰paęž‰peke. Ya bukamanu tonkaęž‰naęž‰ mea aęž‰paaso hataęž‰taęž‰ mo hande hoteke yonkelekemaęž‰ waęž‰paęž‰laęž‰ buka manutaęž‰ otaęž‰ hone na yonkaęž‰lapeke.   
\p
\v 14 Mo kepete kawai wepu halaęž‰ hali Aęž‰lekesaęž‰ndamaęž‰ IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ hoke hau tieke piekeme. Koto ipikaęž‰ pieke haunaęž‰ yenkitaęž‰ Tekehalimaęž‰ anaęž‰naęž‰ halieke.  
\v 15 Mo somemaęž‰ nikaęž‰ walolomaęž‰ pinaęž‰ aęž‰ndaęž‰ wopu liaęž‰me. Kutu pieke handaa neke make hoeyaamaęž‰naęž‰maęž‰ wopu handeteke hapeke.   
\p
\v 16 Mo pi yokaalu pumaęž‰ natenaęž‰taęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ ya puaęž‰ haumanu waluekemaęž‰ titinaęž‰ hombo peaowaęž‰ dinaęž‰taęž‰ mo IĚ± tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰ hali paeyao homeke aęž‰ndaęž‰ na hake iki paeyaomaęž‰ IĚ± minaęž‰paęž‰lao pememe. Kodaęž‰maęž‰ ikaęž‰ pimi hoke hautaęž‰ hone yonkaęž‰laenaęž‰e.  
\v 17 Kutu pimipate mo Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± teke paęž‰taęž‰ hataęž‰ IĚ± wele peayaęž‰me. Kutu piaęž‰ ekimaęž‰taęž‰ mo pi na miki wandaęž‰hali paeyaomaęž‰ opinaęž‰ IĚ±maęž‰ mo Pi Seliapo epeke tupaęž‰ waloaęž‰me. Kutaa make mo laionimaęž‰ IĚ± lu nenaęž‰ taapolo pimikieki teke paęž‰taęž‰ yaęž‰naęž‰ mo Tekehalimaęž‰ IĚ± peteleaęž‰me.  
\v 18 Mo Tekehalimaęž‰ mo hande hoke hau paeyao paęž‰taęž‰ IĚ± yokaęž‰ mea ipikaęž‰ hepeni nane Kilu Tombuao Halaęž‰ ekinaęž‰ epeke tupaęž‰ opolo aęž‰pono lelieke. Mo biki yeiyaęž‰ laasaęž‰eki paeyao ipiki paęž‰taęž‰ na paeyeke pa u haenaęž‰e. Kutu pinaęž‰e.   
\s1 Paeyaaso pimanu  
\p
\v 19 Mo Pisila Akuila yaapo paęž‰taęž‰ make mo Onesipotasinaęž‰ tapake paęž‰taęž‰ tonkaęž‰naęž‰ ya aęž‰talo pi tapaasome.  
\v 20 Etaęž‰situsi ipikitaęž‰ Kotindi da nane hayaęž‰me. Totobimasi yeni hayeke handaa Mailitasi da paęž‰taęž‰ haenaęž‰ epoaęž‰me.  
\v 21 Mo kosaęž‰ ki aĚ±iĚ± na epeke haenaęž‰ kone IĚ± paęž‰taęž‰ aĚ±iĚ± ipuluekemaęž‰ taapo hapeke. Yubulisi Pudenisi Linusi Kolodia make mo mandane Ketiso tapake paeyaomaęž‰ ikaęž‰ aęž‰talo pi neke paęž‰taęž‰ tapaasememe.   
\p
\v 22 Mo Tekehalitaęž‰ nakaęž‰ temoko yaapo hao haenaęž‰e. Kodaęž‰naęž‰ aęž‰taęž‰maęž‰ homa tambaęž‰ minaęž‰laęž‰eki make iki paeyao ameĚ±leĚ± hao haenaęž‰e.   